      "description": "Hey there! I'm parting with my absolute pride and joy, and let me tell you, this beauty is in showroom condition! It\u2019s been pampered since day one and honestly looks and drives like it just rolled off the lot. If you're looking for a ride that\u2019s practically brand new and meticulously cared for, you\u2019ve found it. Come see it for yourself\u2014you won\u2019t be disappointed!",
