      "description": "We are pleased to present this exemplary specimen, maintained to an uncompromising standard that warrants the 'mint' designation. This vehicle exhibits pristine cosmetic integrity and flawless mechanical performance, reflective of a rigorous maintenance pedigree and climate-controlled preservation. For the discerning professional seeking a peerless driving experience, this offering represents the absolute pinnacle of its class.",
      "price": 48750.0,
